item.title: CVE-2022-29093|2024-09-17T04:14:51.831Z -- dell -- supportassist%20client%20commercial
item.description: Dell SupportAssist Client Consumer versions (3.10.4 and versions prior) and Dell SupportAssist Client Commercial versions (3.1.1 and versions prior) contain an arbitrary file deletion vulnerability. Authenticated non-admin user could exploit the issue and delete arbitrary files on the system.
